    • getFromMimeType

      public static String getFromMimeType(String mimeType, Supplier<String> notFound)
      Returns a mime type with a known format reader from the given mime type. Some MIME types are application or vendor specific examples that use a standard underlying format, like XML. There are also examples of synonym types, like "text/csv" and "application/csv" that we want to support.

    • getFromMimeType

      public static String getFromMimeType(String mimeType)
      Returns a mime type with a known format reader from the given mime type. Unknown types are treated as the default. @see #getFromMimeType(String,Supplier)
